Lachlan Murdoch was born on February 16, 1986 in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada as Lachlan Kyle Murdoch. He is an actor, known for Murdoch Mysteries (2008), The Santa Clause (1994) and Papa's Angels (2000).            
